# Design System

## Colors - Adaptive Tokens Only

```typescript
// ✅ ALWAYS - Auto light/dark
'bg-background text-foreground'
'bg-card text-card-foreground'
'bg-primary text-primary-foreground'
'border-border' 'ring-ring'

// ❌ NEVER - Hardcoded colors
'bg-white text-black' 'bg-gray-100' 'bg-[#fff]'
```

## Components - Use Existing Primitives

```typescript
// ✅ Extend existing UI components
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
import { Card, CardContent } from '@/components/ui/card'

// ✅ CVA for variants
const variants = cva(cn('base-classes'), {
  variants: { size: { sm: 'h-8', md: 'h-10' } },
})
```

## Sizing & Spacing

```typescript
// ✅ Size - prefer size-* for equal dimensions
'size-4' // Instead of 'w-4 h-4'
'w-full h-4' // Only when different

// ✅ Spacing - consistent scale
'gap-2 gap-4 gap-6' 'p-2 p-4 p-6' 'py-4 px-3'

// ❌ NEVER arbitrary
'w-4 h-4' 'gap-[12px]' 'p-[18px]'
```

## Custom Utilities - Use When Available

```typescript
'flex-center' // Instead of 'flex items-center justify-center'
'hide-scrollbar' 'container-hypertro' 'safe-area-*'
'masked-placeholder-text' 'shadow-neuro-*'
```

## Loading States - Dedicated Components

```typescript
// ✅ Use existing
import { Skeleton } from '@/components/ui/skeleton'
<Skeleton className="h-4 w-full" />
<Button loading={boolean} />

// ❌ Never custom spinners
<div className="animate-spin border-2" />
```

## Border Radius - Theme Tokens

```typescript
'rounded-sm' // calc(var(--radius) - 4px)
'rounded-lg' // var(--radius) - DEFAULT
```

**Rules**: NEVER deviate from tokens. Check `src/components/ui/` first. All colors must work in light/dark modes automatically.
